rows.label: tlk41300011_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Superbia and Invidia were on the
verge of conflict, weren't they?

rows.label: tlk41300011_03_msg0002
rows.name: But I'm glad a war didn't break out.

rows.label: tlk41300011_03_msg0003
rows.name:
This is all thanks to His
Holiness Marveni's mediation.

rows.label: tlk41300011_03_msg0004
rows.name:
If war had broken out, I might
have had to go back to Gula
and fight for Superbia.

rows.label: tlk41300011_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm really glad it
didn't come to war...
